• Robustness:• Label: Noise, time
sigma = 0.0, tau = 1.0

• Geometry:• Label: Curvature
kappa_c = 0.0  // Euclidean by default



Add assertions to keep these unitless and bounded; document them as conceptual controls, not physical parameters.

